data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story single family home with a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic elegance. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this residence offers a harmonious combination of functionality and aesthetic appeal. With 5 bedrooms and 3 baths, including a convenient first-floor bedroom and bath, this home is designed to cater to various lifestyles and preferences. Please call the agent with any questions.
